ARCTICOS:
    CORE:
        DRIVERS:
            - Allwinner A13 GPIO
            - Quectel EC-21A
            - Audio
            - Frontlight
            - Flashlight
        
        BOOT:
            - UBoot
            - Start services on boot
            - Flashable Images

    SERVICES:
        UI:
            - Finish migrating UI toolkit to display-service
            - Display notifications
            - Interrupt for incoming calls/alarms/reminders
        
        INPUT:
            - Create input service

        TIMING:
            - Create timing service
            - Schedule launch of applications
        
        WATCHDOG:
            - Check status of services 
            - Restart hung services
        
        CELLULAR:
            - Automatically check for incoming calls + messages
            - Notify user via UI service
            - Send messages
            - Start call

    UI:
        - GridView menus
        - Context menus
        - Cursor in getString()
        - Scroll getString() and getMultilineString()

    APPLICATIONS:
        LAUNCHER:
            - Show actual time
            - Show battery percentage
            - Show cellular status 
            - Quickly enter dialer
            - Customize date format
            - Choose between 12-hour & 24-hour time

        CLOCK:
            - Show current time
            - List active alarms
            - Create new alarms and register with timing service

        CALENDAR:
            - Switch between days
            - Quick switch between months
            - Create tasks
            - Register reminders with timing service

        SETTINGS:
            - Load user preferences
            - Assign human-friendly names
            - Let user edit settings
            - Show (non-editable) build information
            - Press build number 8 times to toggle user/basic/developer modes

        MUSIC:
            - Load all music files
            - Sort by album/artist
            - Play in background

        PHONE:
            - List contacts
            - Add contacts
            - Dial by number
            - List previously called numbers
            - Speed Dial

        MESSAGES:
            - List contacts
            - Add contacts
            - Display messages in a thread
            - Send messages

        EMAIL:
            - Refresh recieved emails
            - Send emails
    EMULATOR:
        - Frontlight
        - Flashlight
        - Audio
        - Vibration

    OTHER:
        - USB Tethering
